		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:22px;color:#fab24d"><strong>SOCIAL INTEGRATION COMMISSION</strong></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="center" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/staffing/Images/ncstc_hr_290914.jpg" width="550" height="22" border="0" style="display:block"></td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
		
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>Although you may have been working with The Challenge on the NCS seasonal programmes for years, you might not know about what else we have going on. Alongside the NCS programe delivery and our <a href="https://www.thechallengesociety.org/pages/headstart.html" target="_blank">Head Start</a> and <a href="http://www.stepforward.uk.com/" target="_blank">Step Forward</a> projects for 17-19 year-olds, The Challenge has also set up and sponsored the Social Integration Commission.</p>

<p>The Social Integration Commission is investigating how far the UK is socially divided for culture, ethnicity, age and wealth, and the impact this has on our society. The Commission's three reports have now all been published, and are already sparking discussion in the media - if you'd like to know more about the Social Integration Commision, <a href="http://socialintegrationcommission.org.uk/index.php" target="_blank">head to it's website!</a></p>
			
			
			<td align="right" valign="top"><img src="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/social%20integration%20commission.JPG" alt="" width="200" height="225" border="0"></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>
		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
